Package org.ivoa.dm.vosi.availability

package org.ivoa.dm.vosi.availability
package VOSIAvail. A schema for formatting availability metadata as returned by an availability resource defined in the IVOA Support Interfaces specification (VOSI). See http://www.ivoa.net/Documents/latest/VOSI.html.
